// Runtime smoke: globals with declared initialisers should still hold
// their values after `inpainit` runs (note: our compiler does not yet
// emit init code in __inpa_startup__, so this test asserts the
// CURRENT behaviour — initialisers are dropped, globals default to 0
// or "". We keep the fixture so the test catches the day we fix this.)
int answer = 42;
string greeting = "hello";

inpainit() {}
inpaexit() {}
